OL,6,FWhat she experienced in the grounds of
OL,7,Fthe picturesque 18th century Georgian
OL,8,Fhouse, surrounded by woodland and
OL,9,Fquaint cottages, still haunts her to
OL,10,Fthis day.
OL,12,FMs Rodden, now 88, described the home
OL,13,Fas a "slave camp" where they were
OL,14,F"forced to do laundry for the staff
OL,15,Fand villagers" and scrub the flag
OL,16,Fstones in the building whilst heavily
OL,17,Fpregnant.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
