OL,6,FMs Rodden, who delivered a tearful
OL,7,Fspeech at the unveiling of the plaque,
OL,8,Fwas forced to give up her baby son,
OL,9,FMark.
OL,11,FFor 50 years, all she had to remember
OL,12,Fhim by was a blurry photo the size of
OL,13,Fa postage stamp. The pair were finally
OL,14,Freunited after Mark tracked her down
OL,15,Fas an adult.
OL,17,FDr Phil Frampton, who organised the
OL,18,Fevent and was born at the same home in
OL,19,F1953, said the plaque offered
OL,20,Fsurvivors the "opportunity to develop
OL,21,Fa sense of healing".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
