OL,6,F"Today's unveiling in commemoration of
OL,7,Fthe survivors and victims of the
OL,8,FRosemundy Home was incredible and
OL,9,Fbeyond our best expectations," he told
OL,10,FITV News.
OL,12,F"Some birth mothers came from across
OL,13,Fthe south of England and one adult
OL,14,Fadoptee flew in from her home in
OL,15,FPortugal. The intense emotion of the
OL,16,Fsurvivors ... their relief, tears of
OL,17,Fjoy and sense of healing, was there
OL,18,Ffor all to see."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
