OL,6,FThe unveiling at the former site of
OL,7,FRosemundy Mother and Baby Home in St
OL,8,FAgnes, Cornwall, was attended by
OL,9,Fmothers, adult adoptees and campaigners
OL,11,FDr Frampton spent his childhood in
OL,12,Fcare, describing the mistreatment and
OL,13,Fracism he faced growing up as "cruel".
OL,15,FHe has been fighting for decades for
OL,16,Frecognition of his experience and for
OL,17,Fa public acknowledgement of what his
OL,18,Fmother, who died aged 32, went through.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
