OL,6,FSpeaking after the plaque unveiling,
OL,7,Fhe said: "I feel proud of the women
OL,8,Fand adoptee survivors, and incredibly
OL,9,Fpleased at the thought that hundreds
OL,10,Fof thousands of affected families will
OL,11,Ftoday have more than a glimmer of
OL,12,Flight at the end of one long, often
OL,13,Fdark, tunnel."
OL,15,FSurvivors and campaigners are calling
OL,16,Fon the government to formally
OL,17,Fapologise for the state's role in
OL,18,Finstitutions like Rosemundy Home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
