OL,6,F"Why is this five letter word so hard
OL,7,Ffor the government to say?" Ms Rodden
OL,8,Fsaid. "Sorry. Why is that so
OL,9,Fdifficult?"
OL,11,FIn 2021, an inquiry by the Joint
OL,12,FCommittee of Human Rights concluded
OL,13,Fthat the state bore ultimate
OL,14,Fresponsibility for the suffering
OL,15,Finflicted on vulnerable women and
OL,16,Ftheir children, calling on the
OL,17,Fgovernment to issue an official
OL,18,Fapology. Four years later, survivors
OL,19,Fare still waiting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
