OL,6,F"The government's failure to act on
OL,7,Fthe forced adoption scandal raises
OL,8,Fhuge questions about where social
OL,9,Fjustice is going in this country," Dr
OL,10,FFrampton added.
OL,12,FThe group Movement for an Adoption
OL,13,FApology (MAA) echo these calls, and
OL,14,Falso want specialist support for those
OL,15,Faffected including trauma informed
OL,16,Fcounselling services, help with
OL,17,Freunions and tracing as well as easier
OL,18,Faccess to historical records.
