OL,6,F"To those who have suffered, we once
OL,7,Fagain offer our heartfelt sorrow and
OL,8,Fregret. While such decisions may have
OL,9,Fbeen considered appropriate by many at
OL,10,Fthe time, society now recognises the
OL,11,Fprofound and lasting impact they have
